<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-18355] HTTP component overwrites basic authentication credentials with proxy authentication </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-18355</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We use HTTP endpoints with basic authentication (params &lt;tt&gt;authUsername&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;authPassword&lt;/tt&gt;) via a proxy that requires proxy authentication (params &lt;tt&gt;proxyAuthUsername&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;proxyAuthPassword&lt;/tt&gt;).&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But basic authentication fails. In debug logs we see that basic authentication header is using proxy credentials. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13475303">CAMEL-18355</key>
            <summary>HTTP component overwrites basic authentication credentials with proxy authentication </summary>
